org.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN watchers ON watchers.watchable_id = issues.id AND watchers.watchable_type = "$1" WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking') IS NOT NULL AND watchers.user_id = 1

rewrites.sql: SELECT issues.* FROM issues INNER JOIN projects ON projects.id = issues.project_id INNER JOIN watchers ON watchers.watchable_id = issues.id AND watchers.watchable_type = "$1" WHERE projects.status <> 9 AND (SELECT 1 AS one FROM enabled_modules AS em WHERE em.project_id = projects.id AND em.name = 'issue_tracking' LIMIT 1) IS NOT NULL AND watchers.user_id = 1
